title: Statement at the 7th FOREST EUROPE Ministerial Conference (Ministry of Culture of the Kingdom of ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Culture of the Kingdom of Norway ) Excellencies, ladies and gentlemen, dear FOREST EUROPE colleagues, First of all, I would like to thank the Spanish government for arranging this conference here in the city of Madrid .
